        "value": 50,
        "unit": "%",
        "description": "Ensures uniform coverage; 50% optimal for SiGe to avoid gaps or hot spots given beam divergence at 1064 nm. Source: Process optimization studies in Opt. Express (2020) for scanned laser cleaning of alloys."
